<!-- gdm_configuration_files-intro-00 -->
    <div id="gdm_configuration_files-intro-00" style="position: absolute; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translate3d(4000px, -1500px, 0px) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) scale(1); transform-style: preserve-3d; "  class="step slide past" data-x="4000" data-y="-1500">

     <div style="width: 90%;  position: absolute; top: 20px; text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:200%;">gdm configuration files</p><p style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:20px;"> </p></div>

<div style="position: absolute; top: 200px; left:100px; right:100px; text-align:left; font-size:100%;">

<ul>
<li style="list-style:disc;">'gdm' staat voor <u>g</u>nome <u>d</u>isplay <u>m</u>anager</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">GNOME is een van de belangrijkste GUIs (<u>G</u>raphical <u>U</u>ser <u>I</u>nterface)</li> 
<li style="list-style:disc;">De basis is te installeren met 'apt-get install gdm' of 'yum install gdm'</li>
</ul>
</div>

	<div id="container" style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; font-size:40%;">
  		<div id="left"><a href="http://www.linuxamsterdam.nl" target="_blank"><img src="la.svg" width=204px height=68px></a></div>
  		<div id="right"><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" target="_blank"><img src="cc_by-sa.svg" width=88px height=31px></a></div>
  		<div id="center">LPIC-1 | Section 106.2 | Page 6/20</div>  

	</div>
</div>
<!-- gdm_configuration_files-intro-01 -->
    <div id="gdm_configuration_files-intro-01" style="position: absolute; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translate3d(5000px, -1500px, 0px) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) scale(1); transform-style: preserve-3d; "  class="step slide past" data-x="5000" data-y="-1500">

     <div style="width: 90%;  position: absolute; top: 20px; text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:200%;">gdm configuration files</p><p style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:20px;"> </p></div>

<div style="position: absolute; top: 200px; left:100px; right:100px; text-align:left; font-size:100%;">
<ul>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Als je meerdere Graphische interfaces hebt geinstalleerd kan je kiezen met welke gestart wordt.</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">In Ubuntu staat dit in '/etc/X11/default-display-manager' en daar staat default '/usr/bin/gdm'</li> 
<li style="list-style:disc;">In CentOS is dit te wijzigen in '/etc/sysconfig/desktop' </li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">GNOME bepaal je door dit toe te voegen: DISPLAYMANAGER="GNOME"</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Heb je geen '/etc/sysconfig/desktop' dan kan je deze zelf aanmaken.</li>
</ul>
</div>

	<div id="container" style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; font-size:40%;">
  		<div id="left"><a href="http://www.linuxamsterdam.nl" target="_blank"><img src="la.svg" width=204px height=68px></a></div>
  		<div id="right"><a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" target="_blank"><img src="cc_by-sa.svg" width=88px height=31px></a></div>
  		<div id="center">LPIC-1 | Section 106.2 | Page 7/20</div>  

	</div>
</div>
<!-- gdm_configuration_files-intro-02 -->
    <div id="gdm_configuration_files-intro-02" style="position: absolute; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translate3d(6000px, -1500px, 0px) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) scale(1); transform-style: preserve-3d; "  class="step slide past" data-x="6000" data-y="-1500">

     <div style="width: 90%;  position: absolute; top: 20px; text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:200%;">gdm configuration files</p><p style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:20px;"> </p></div>

<div style="position: absolute; top: 200px; left:100px; right:100px; text-align:left; font-size:100%;">
<ul>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Je kan in oudere GNOME versies bijvoorbeeld het welkomsbericht wijzigen.</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Wijzigingen doe je in deze file '/etc/gdm/custom.conf'</li> 
<li style="list-style:disc;">Om een welkomstbericht te wijzigen voeg je toe:</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Greeter=/usr/libexec/gdmlogin # onder [daemon]</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">DefaultWelcome=false # onder [greeter]</li>
<li style="list-style:disc;">Welcome=Authorized users only! # onder [greeter]</li>
</ul>
</div>

	<div id="container" style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; font-size:40%;">
